    Direct Known Subclasses:
    SimpleMultisetProperty
    public abstract class MultisetPropertyBase<E>
extends MultisetProperty<E>
    Abstract base class for implementing a Property wrapping an ObservableMultiset.

    This class provides identical functionality for Multiset as MapPropertyBase for Map, SetPropertyBase for Set, or ListPropertyBase for List.
